title: GTA Online: Money Fronts
headline: GTA Online: Money Fronts
subtitle: Now Available
content:
From the frenzied clubs of Tony Prince to El Rubio's narcotrafficking empire, the power of Epsilon to the gold-tinted hijinks of Yusuf Amir — they’re all sustained by one thing: dirty filthy money. And you've just been summoned by the man who oversees it all.

Welcome to a world of corruption. Channel new revenue streams of clean and dirty income through iconic local businesses in Money Fronts — now available in GTA Online.
